snippet.title: Maz Jobrani and Luenell Campbell on Amber Rose’s Bush Nude Photo, Celeb Break-Ins & Political Comedy
snippet.description:
No topic was off limits on Sway in the Morning when comedians Maz Jobrani and Luenell Campbell stopped by the show. We heard their thoughts about Amber Rose’s ‘bring back the bush’ Instagram pic, perceptions of sexuality in America and so much more.

We talked to Jobrani about his experience in the CBS sitcom 'Superior Donuts.' The Iranian-American comedian also spoke to us about being unapologetic about his political opinions during this sensitive climate.

We also got to hear from Campbell about her nude photoshoot for Penthouse Magazine. She tells us that she relished the opportunity to empower women her age. In fact, her goal is to see one of those photos on New York’s jumbotron when she get’s her Netflix special.
